      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't feel metaphorical, it feels biological. it's like my processing speed is just... higher. and i've been reading about how certain types of high-energy particles can cause localized epigenetic changes. if a solar flare hit the atmosphere with enough intensity, couldn't it actually trigger a rapid adaptive response in certain neural pathways? i feel like i'm finally operating at my actual potential.",
